Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.83,0:00:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}The dreams embraced by a single life{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.84,0:00:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}are boundless beyond even the stars.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.84,0:00:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}The dreams that we foster over time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.85,0:00:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}are waiting for the moment{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}when we come upon them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.53,0:00:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}The words we exchange{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}make our hearts tremble,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.53,0:00:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}and a chance meeting{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}could change the future.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.21,0:01:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}People, no matter who they are,{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}as they pursue their dreams,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.48,0:01:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}have the courage to travel new paths.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.15,0:01:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}As we leave behind a\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}living testament of our journey,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.49,0:01:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}the Galaxy Railways on which we travel{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}continue ever on.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.51,0:01:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}People have long believed in things they{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}could not see, relying on them to live.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.85,0:01:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Love, relationships, minds...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.53,0:01:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Each of these is something that{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}can neither be seen nor touched.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.47,0:02:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Thank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.82,0:02:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Ta-kun,{\i0} don't stay in here,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}let's go have fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.15,0:02:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.15,0:02:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.49,0:02:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}The truth is, my business has failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.49,0:02:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I boarded this train as a final gamble.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}I've blown all the money I had on hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.83,0:02:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Hold on, {\i1}Ta-kun,{\i0} are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.17,0:02:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Once we get back, I'll start over\N{\c&He1e1e1&}from the beginning again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.24,0:02:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}With that in mind, do you\N{\c&He1e1e1&}still want to hang out with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.18,0:02:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You've got to be kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.01,0:02:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}If you've lost everything,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}what does that leave you with?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.85,0:02:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Just a homely face\N{\c&He1e1e1&}and stunted legs, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.85,0:02:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm not giving this bag\N{\c&He1e1e1&}back to you, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.86,0:02:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Spurned by another woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.53,0:02:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Bartender-san,{\i0} the usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.53,0:03:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}- Very well.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}- {\i1}Conductor-san...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.80,0:03:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Thank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.14,0:03:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Looks like your prospects\N{\c&He1e1e1&}didn't pan out again, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.81,0:03:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm just not cut out to be a rich man.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.81,0:03:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Hey, {\i1}Oyama-san,{\i0} you'll come\N{\c&He1e1e1&}across an angelic lady someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.48,0:03:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You're such a nice person.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}If only you could drink alcohol, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.15,0:03:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}If this will do, I'll join you anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.83,0:03:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Well then, cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.51,0:03:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What are those?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.85,0:03:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}They appear to be pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.51,0:03:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Pirates!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.85,0:03:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Headquarters!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.80,0:04:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Grace Wealthy{\i0} has derailed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.13,0:04:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Send a rescue team at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.30,0:04:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}"Sexaroid"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.47,0:04:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I've never seen a train\N{\c&He1e1e1&}like this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.48,0:04:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}That's the galactic excursion\N{\c&He1e1e1&}train {\i1}Grace Wealthy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.48,0:04:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}It's the Galaxy Railways'\N{\c&He1e1e1&}publicly managed casino train,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.72,0:04:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}which doesn't have regular service,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}and takes a different line each trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.82,0:04:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Casino?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.15,0:04:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I've always wanted to take\N{\c&He1e1e1&}a ride on it once myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.54,0:04:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Planet Green, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.20,0:04:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}They sure found a nasty place\N{\c&He1e1e1&}to drop in on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.21,0:04:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}The atmosphere and ground on\N{\c&He1e1e1&}this planet corrodes any kind of metal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.55,0:05:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Even with the anticorrosive\N{\c&He1e1e1&}coating on SDF trains,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.48,0:05:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}they calculate that we'll only\N{\c&He1e1e1&}be able to last about six hours here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.49,0:05:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}An ordinary passenger train\N{\c&He1e1e1&}won't last long at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.49,0:05:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}There's a metallic reading coming\N{\c&He1e1e1&}from the floor of a dense forest
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.03,0:05:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}about fifty kilos to the east.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.18,0:05:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Captain, please let me go, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.85,0:05:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}No, you stay put today. The environment\N{\c&He1e1e1&}here will be hazardous to your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.19,0:05:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I will be okay if I put on\N{\c&He1e1e1&}a protective suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.69,0:05:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}There could be some wounded\N{\c&He1e1e1&}that need urgent care.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.87,0:05:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We've spotted the downed train\N{\c&He1e1e1&}and survivors. Moving in to rescue them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.54,0:06:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yuki, be sure to double-check all\N{\c&He1e1e1&}the linkages on your protective suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.48,0:06:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.82,0:06:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Hey! SDF! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.15,0:06:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Hurry it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.50,0:06:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You took long enough, you idiots!\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.17,0:06:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.51,0:06:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What are you doing!? Please calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.84,0:06:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Don't be ridiculous! How can you\N{\c&He1e1e1&}expect us to calm down!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.18,0:06:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.18,0:06:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Easy, Yuuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.53,0:06:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}They came this close to dying.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Don't rub them the wrong way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.20,0:06:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}B- but still...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.53,0:06:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I am all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.87,0:07:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Please do not rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.14,0:07:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}So this is the casino train\N{\c&He1e1e1&}I've been longing to ride, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.82,0:07:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.82,0:07:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Hey, you guys from the SDF!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.16,0:07:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Stay with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.50,0:07:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Conductor-san,{\i0} hang in there!\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Hang tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.50,0:07:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Bruce, we've found a crewmember.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.84,0:07:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You've got to help him, fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.84,0:07:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}O- {\i1}Oyama-san,{\i0} I'm done for...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.84,0:07:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What are you talking about!\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Don't say things like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.84,0:07:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Take care... Oyama... - {\i1}san...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.18,0:07:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Hey, {\i1}Conductor-san!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.13,0:08:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Your shoulder is dislocated.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Let me treat that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.14,0:08:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}For mechanical beings and androids,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}this is a planet of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.49,0:08:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Damn those pirates,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}coming and robbing us of everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.16,0:08:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}The Galaxy Railways had better\N{\c&He1e1e1&}compensate us for everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.16,0:08:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}They're surprisingly petty people, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.17,0:08:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Louis!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.50,0:08:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Mission accomplished.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Returning to {\i1}Big One.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.51,0:08:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Um, you're {\i1}Oyama-san,{\i0} right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.85,0:08:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.19,0:09:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.46,0:09:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I am Yuuki Manabu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.13,0:09:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I see. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.47,0:09:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What are we doing!?\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Hurry up and get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.81,0:09:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Taking off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.48,0:09:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What's wrong!? Trouble with the engines?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.15,0:09:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}No, it's the overload alarm!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.49,0:09:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What? Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.50,0:09:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}It's an indigenous creature!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.83,0:09:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Maximum output! Shake it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.17,0:09:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.51,0:09:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.18,0:09:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.19,0:10:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.19,0:10:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.20,0:10:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}- {\i1}Oyama-san!{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&}- Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.88,0:10:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.89,0:10:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What a disaster!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.89,0:10:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.24,0:10:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Setting us down...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.24,0:10:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Wait, you can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.57,0:10:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You can't mean that! Why not!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.91,0:11:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We'll all end up dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.85,0:11:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Yuuki-san...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.85,0:11:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.52,0:11:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Get the passengers to {\i1}Big One,{\i0} quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.53,0:11:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yuki, I'm dropping\N{\c&He1e1e1&}some weapons down to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.86,0:11:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.87,0:11:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.20,0:11:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yuuki, David and Louis have returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.14,0:11:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm having them unload and\N{\c&He1e1e1&}am sending them back there right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.21,0:11:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Copy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.55,0:11:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Launch preparations complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.55,0:11:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.56,0:11:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Are you all right, {\i1}Oyama-san?{\i0} It's too\N{\c&He1e1e1&}dangerous here. Let's move at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.52,0:12:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm all right. Let's hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.19,0:12:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}David, Louis, I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.55,0:12:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I can't locate Yuki and the passenger.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.22,0:12:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Call them on the radio.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.89,0:13:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yuuki, don't forget about how long\N{\c&He1e1e1&}your coating will hold out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.83,0:13:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.17,0:13:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yuki, come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.51,0:13:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Where are you, Yuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.51,0:13:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Damn! We're not getting\N{\c&He1e1e1&}anywhere from the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.18,0:13:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}David, take the east side of the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.85,0:13:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.19,0:13:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Hurry and get this train moving!\N{\c&He1e1e1&}What are they doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.20,0:13:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}If it's money they want,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}I'll pay anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.88,0:13:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}This is Yuki. {\i1}Big One,{\i0} please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.50,0:14:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Are you coming around?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.50,0:14:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Have you been with me this whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.50,0:14:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}How come you're being so nice?\N{\c&He1e1e1&}You even dove after me earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.58,0:14:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I haven't had a chance to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.51,0:14:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}It is my duty, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.51,0:14:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You don't often find people\N{\c&He1e1e1&}who will go this far out of duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.89,0:14:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You're a wonderful person.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.52,0:14:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}That's the way I was made.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.19,0:14:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Oh, right, that's the way\N{\c&He1e1e1&}people should be by nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.86,0:14:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You and my mom are the only ones\N{\c&He1e1e1&}who have ever been this nice to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.20,0:14:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You're the first pretty young lady\N{\c&He1e1e1&}I've met that's like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.87,0:14:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Ever since I've been a kid,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}I've led an unremarkable life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.88,0:14:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}But as soon as I struck cosmonite\N{\c&He1e1e1&}on my home planet, that turned around.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.55,0:14:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}However, as a result...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.22,0:15:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}As a result?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.48,0:15:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Nah, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.49,0:15:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}But then, I can't believe there are\N{\c&He1e1e1&}people like you out there in the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.82,0:15:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Um, I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.49,0:15:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}And here, at the very end,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}I meet someone who really is nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.83,0:15:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Um, {\i1}Oyama-san,{\i0} I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.50,0:15:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Please don't give up.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Let's get out of here alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.10,0:15:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}My friends will surely come save us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.18,0:15:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}This is Yuki. {\i1}Big One,{\i0} please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.52,0:15:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Say, {\i1}Yuki- san...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.85,0:15:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.52,0:15:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}If we do get out of here alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.19,0:15:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Aw, never mind. You must have\N{\c&He1e1e1&}a boyfriend or two already.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.86,0:15:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Unless, I suppose,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}you're already married?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.87,0:15:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What's the matter, {\i1}Oyama-san?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.54,0:15:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I must have been talking too much...\N{\c&He1e1e1&}The oxygen here is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.48,0:16:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm breathing easier...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.49,0:16:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I am a sexaroid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.49,0:16:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm not human.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.16,0:16:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Please hold your breath\N{\c&He1e1e1&}as much as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.17,0:16:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}The concentration of oxygen\N{\c&He1e1e1&}in the atmosphere on this planet
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.90,0:16:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}is extremely high,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}which causes you to hyperventilate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.51,0:16:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}If you have trouble with it again,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}please don't hesitate to tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.17,0:16:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I can counteract it for a short period.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.51,0:16:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}T- that's easy for you to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.51,0:16:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm sure my friends from the SDF are\N{\c&He1e1e1&}searching for us. Let's stay outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.19,0:16:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}W- what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.19,0:16:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Don't talk too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.53,0:16:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}The corrosion is spreading.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.20,0:16:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}My body is mechanical,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.06,0:16:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}so if this keeps up, I will\N{\c&He1e1e1&}end up like that conductor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.48,0:17:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Everyone, return!\N{\c&He1e1e1&}We can't wait any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.82,0:17:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}The blame is entirely on me\N{\c&He1e1e1&}for sending Yuki out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.16,0:17:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Captain, a little while longer...\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Please wait a little while longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.50,0:17:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yuuki! Don't go acting on your own!\N{\c&He1e1e1&}We're heading back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.83,0:17:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Manabu, it's too dangerous\N{\c&He1e1e1&}to wait any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.50,0:17:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Please, just a little longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.17,0:17:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yuuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.17,0:17:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I don't want to let one\N{\c&He1e1e1&}of our dear friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.17,0:17:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}and that other nice person, die here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.51,0:17:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I know how you feel, but the corrosion\N{\c&He1e1e1&}on the hull won't wait for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.85,0:17:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Do you want to get the passengers\N{\c&He1e1e1&}and the rest of us killed, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.18,0:17:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yuuki, this is an order.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.85,0:17:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.86,0:17:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Yuuki-kun...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.14,0:18:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Oyama-san!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.49,0:18:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Yuuki... - san...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.16,0:18:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Yuki-san!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.83,0:18:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.17,0:18:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Yuuki...san!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.84,0:18:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Captain, {\i1}Yuuki-kun{\i0} and\N{\c&He1e1e1&}the others have returned!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.85,0:18:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Everyone is all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.85,0:18:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}All right, we're moving out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.13,0:19:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You've got to be joking! You delayed\N{\c&He1e1e1&}our departure over a lousy robot!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.80,0:19:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What were you thinking!? You can\N{\c&He1e1e1&}replace those things again and again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.14,0:19:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Manabu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.14,0:19:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You platoon members can't\N{\c&He1e1e1&}lay a hand on us passengers...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.81,0:19:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Oyama-san...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.82,0:19:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Are you... serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.82,0:19:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.16,0:19:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Oyama-san...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.49,0:19:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You are human!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.16,0:19:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}That's just an illusion you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.60,0:19:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I am a medical unit, governed by\N{\c&He1e1e1&}an artificial intelligence.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.50,0:19:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.50,0:19:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Then why do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.17,0:19:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}In my world, you're a human.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}The kindest woman in the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.84,0:19:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Are you... in love with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.51,0:20:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yuuki Manabu. He's a good man.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.52,0:20:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Such a thing... isn't possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.52,0:20:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}However, there is something\N{\c&He1e1e1&}I think about.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.53,0:20:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I have inherited the looks and\N{\c&He1e1e1&}personality of a certain woman from Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.53,0:20:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}It is possible that somewhere\N{\c&He1e1e1&}in her memories,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.80,0:20:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}there was a man that she loved deeply,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}and that he resembles.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.22,0:20:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}How is Yuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.55,0:20:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Right... Once we get back,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.39,0:20:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}and she gets an overhaul and\N{\c&He1e1e1&}some parts replaced, she'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.23,0:20:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.90,0:20:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Young man!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.23,0:20:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Take good care of {\i1}Yuki-san{\i0} for me!\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Take care of her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.91,0:21:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}There are things which are important{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}that can never be seen with the eye.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.18,0:21:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}For those that believe in them,{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}they are truly there.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.85,0:21:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}And for those that believe in them,{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}they can touch them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.20,0:21:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}With a heart that is pure.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.21,0:21:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}How many nights have I\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}spent alone since then?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.23,0:22:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Constantly having dreams of the hope{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}that you are, as I lightly sleep.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.91,0:22:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}The smiles and tears that{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}you gave to me and me alone{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.92,0:22:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}come to mind every time{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}I get disheartened,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.26,0:22:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}and I set forth again toward the morrow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.93,0:22:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}The joyful light of{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}the galaxy beckons me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.54,0:22:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}to that beloved person within my heart.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.54,0:22:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}No matter how far apart we are,{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}my memories will never fade.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.22,0:23:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}My heart wishes always{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}to be at your side.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.57,0:23:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Planet Haaga Loo, a world bound{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}by snow and ice.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.91,0:23:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}On this planet, with its legendary{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Blue Flame of Isperil, I'm going to...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.91,0:23:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Next time on Tales of the{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Galaxy Railways, Episode 17:{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&}"Armored Goddess"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.25,0:23:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}We're going to encounter{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}something at the next station.{\i0}